  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d91\u0db1 \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dba \u0d85\u0dc4\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dab\u0dd2\u0dba \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7 - \u0db8\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dbb\u0db4\u0dad\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The daughter who went to ask the date of the arrival of petrol died - the mother is serious",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Anuradhapura police said that a mother and daughter who came to a petrol station in Pandulagama area on a motorcycle to find out the next date of petrol delivery, collided with a tipper truck that had come to get fuel.",
        "Police say that the person who unfortunately lost her life is a 36-year-old woman named PD Anoma Ranasinghe, resident of Sravastipura, Olayawa.",
        "The police say that the mother of the deceased, who was seriously injured, is being treated in the intensive care unit of the Anuradhapura Teaching Hospital.",
        "The police say that the accident occurred when a tipper truck, which had been stopped in front of the gas station for several days to get diesel, had a dead battery, and another tipper truck came and pushed the rear part of the other tipper truck.",
        "The deceased came with her mother and asked the filling station when the fuel would return and when she was about to go back on her motorcycle, the tipper suddenly started up and collided with the motorcycle carrying the mother and daughter, the police said.",
        "The driver of the tipper involved in the accident was arrested and he was to be produced in court."
      ],
